modelVersions.name: Hanfu_weijin_NewVersion
modelVersions.description:
鉴于很多人反馈说高权重下很高概率无头，故发布了这个新版本。新版本在高权重下无头的概率大大降低（相同长宽比的情况下），LORA权重为0.9时，无头概率从83%降低到了33%，新版本权重在0.8以下时，无头情况基本不会出现（以上数据的测试模型为majic）。但在生成全身图时，最好依旧将长宽比设置为2：1左右

新版本关键词：1girl,floral print, (blue/white/red/black/yellow/pink print chinese shirt),(pink/yellow/blue/white/red/black print long skirt),

Lora权重：0.6~0.8

————————————————————————————————————————

This is the new version of Hanfu_weijin, it has a much lower probability of headlessness at high weights. The probability of headlessness has been reduced from 83% to 33% at weights of 0.9. And headlessness is largely absent at weights below 0.8 in the new version (The test checkpoint is majic). However, it is best to still set the aspect ratio to around 2:1 when you're going to generate a full-body img

Trigger words of this version：1girl,floral print, (blue/white/red/black/yellow/pink print chinese shirt),(pink/yellow/blue/white/red/black print long skirt),

Lora's weight：0.6~0.8
